title: Google Home and Pixel 5 conflict
content:
Lately, my Pixel 5 has been responding to commands in addition to the Google Home device that I'm actually talking to. It runs routines, sets timers, etc, simultaneously with the Google Home. 
Yes, both the phone and Google Home is set up on the same account, and my Google app is up to date.
category: Google Assistant and Voice Actions, Google Pixel 5
